Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on developing a system for learning legged locomotion policies with deep RL in the real world on a Minitaur robot. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses deep reinforcement learning (deep RL) as a promising method for developing control policies autonomously. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep RL to develop a system for learning legged locomotion policies with minimal human effort. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): Although not the main focus, the paper may involve computer vision techniques for data collection and analysis. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the development of a safety-constrained RL framework for on-robot learning systems.
